title: Data Privacy/Hacking
comment: Due to the implant being new, it is unlikely that they can make the security flawless. This could lead to hackers.

title: Reduces Accidents
comment: Can reduce fatigue and tiredness, so will decrease accidents such as traffic accidents.

title: Class System
comment: The implant could create a rich/poor class system with people who do and people who don't have the implant.

title: Increased Killing
comment: Could make military soldiers more likely to cause violence or murder in the line of duty.

title: Drug Replacement
comment: The implant could replace the need for certain medication, producing a cheaper and easier use of medication.

title: Money Making by companies
comment: The implant could create ways of big corporations making money from the implants and implementing unwanted features or preying upon people with the implant.

title: Unknown Factors
comment: There are still many unknown factors, which could be good or bad, and these are not yet known.

title: Regulates Sleep Cycle
comment: Can help people reduce fatigue and tiredness, and can help reduce accidents.

title: Decomposes when no longer wanted
comment: When the implant is no longer needed, the implant decomposes without need for any operation to remove.

title: Energy Efficient/No Maintenance
comment: No Power needed, so runs itself. No dangerous power systems running in your head.

title: App Controllable
comment: The implant is app controlled, this could be good or bad depending on who has access to control the implant.

title: Easily Implanted
comment: Non invasive to implant in the head.

title: Small in size
comment: Implant is small, so can easily be implanted and doesn't take lots of room.

title: technological implant
comment: The positives and negatives of a brain implant.
